<link
  href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat"
  rel="stylesheet"
  type="text/css"
/>
<div
  style="width:100%;background:#DDEDFD;padding:60px 0px;font-family:Montserrat;color:#404040;"
>
  <table
    border="0"
    cellpadding="0"
    cellspacing="0"
    width="800"
    style="float:none;margin:0 auto;background:#FFF;"
  >
    <tr>
      <th style="background:#6F63C3;padding:10px;">
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
          <tr>
            <td width="60">
              <img
                src="https://poolfunders.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/PF-Logo-hexa-1.png"
                style="width:100%;height:60px;overflow:hidden;"
              />
            </td>
            <td>
              <h1
                style="line-height:60px;margin:0px;padding:0px;margin-left:20px;color:#FFF;"
              >
                The Pool Founders
              </h1>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding:20px;">
        <h3 style="color:#010101;font-size:22px;line-height:30px;">
          <span style=" border-bottom:1px solid #010101;"
            >Contract Terms of the projects:</span
          >
        </h3>
        <div><p>tx-hash: <%= details.transactionHash %></p></div>
        <div style="margin-top:30px;line-height:28px;font-size:15px;">
          <p>
            This contract is between <b><%= details.proCreatorName %></b>, from
            <b><%= details.proCreatorAdd %></b> with email
            <b><%= details.proCreatorEmail%></b>, phone
            <b><%= details.proCreatorPhone%></b> and pan
            <b><%= details.proCreatorPan%></b>
          </p>
          <p><strong>And</strong></p>
          <p><b><%= details.investorName %></b> having contact details as</p>
          <p><strong>To certify that :</strong></p>
          <p>
            <b><%= details.investorName %></b> has invested the amount of INR
            <b><%= details.paymentAmount %></b> to back this the project
            <b><%= details.projectName %></b> and therefore, is entitled to
            receive share of <b><%= details.share %>%</b> and convertable
            <b><%= details.conv %>%</b>
          </p>
        </div>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding:20px;">
        <h3>With condition that:</h3>

        <table
          border="0"
          width="100%"
          cellpadding="0"
          cellspacing="0"
          style="line-height:28px;font-size:15px;"
        >
          <tr>
            <td width="20" valign="top"><strong>1.</strong></td>
            <td valign="top">
              The convertibles notes will be paid back at 8% yearly interest
              after three years, albeit company is profitable by the end of
              third year.
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td colspan="2" style="padding:15px 0px;text-align:center;">
              <strong>OR</strong>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td width="10" valign="top"><strong>2.</strong></td>
            <td valign="top">
              May be converted into common shares (as a dynamically calculated
              percentage quota out of 10% allocated venture capitalist share for
              this funding goal) as per share capital distribution model
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding:20px;">
        <h3>Payment release:</h3>
        <p style="line-height:28px;font-size:15px;">
          There will be an escrow account for every investor where the money
          will be kept after investments and will be disbursed to
          startup/projects only when they reach certain promised milestone as
          per payment release clause given below
        </p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
        <p style="line-height:28px;font-size:15px;">
          To protect backers/investors interest and money, Poolfunders has
          defined a workflow where money would be released in three stages
        </p>
        <ul style="line-height:28px;font-size:15px;margin:25px 0px;">
          <li style="margin-bottom:15px;">
            First stage: 25% release after the campaign has ended on PoolFunders
            platform.
          </li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:15px;">
            Second stage: 40% once the first milestone has been met and fund
            utilisation has been made in proper use. (check:Funds approval
            process)
          </li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:15px;">
            Third stage: 35% once the Second milestone has been met in
            accordance with proper fund utilisations. (check:Funds approval
            process)
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p style="line-height:28px;font-size:15px;">
          Failure to meet any of the above KPIs would result in the refund of
          remaining money, at that stage, back to investors.
        </p>
        <p style="line-height:28px;font-size:15px;">
          Also note that, if the idea of product/service for which campaign is
          started turns out to be copyright infringed, then the funding
          remaining amount would be returned back to investor and Owner will be
          blacklisted from our platform and may get possible chances of legal
          action.
        </p>
        <p style="line-height:28px;font-size:15px;">
          And finally, you understand that investing in startups are highly
          risky and you may lose part or all of your amount if your invested
          startups fails
        </p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding:10px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td
        style="background:#34495E;padding:30px 0px;text-align:center;color:#FFF;"
      >
        <p>Copyright Â© 2020 The Pool Funders. All Rights Reserved.</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>
